cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.DS 

This paper discusses recent advances in collaborative filtering and ranking, which are topics related to information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
